            <h3>What are cookies?</h3>
            <p>A cookie is a small file of dataletters and numbers we store on your browser or your computer or other internet enabled mobile device such as a smartphone or tablet. A cookie will usually contain the name of the website from which the cookie has come, the "lifetime" of the cookie (i.e. how long it will remain on your device) and a value, which is usually a randomly generated unique number.</p>
